item.title: (Hu)go Template Primer
item.description: layout: post title: What is Chemistry? Playoffs in the NBA just started, and I hear reporters on the news talking about chemistry all the time. However, what exactly is chemistry? What determines if teammates have good chemistry? I decide to google “NBA Chemistry”, and the consensus online is “chemistry”, is actually really hard to define, because it is not quantified yet. So, how do you measure chemistry, when it could mean a million different variables.
